					<p><img src="/img/sm-book.jpg" alt="book"/>Advanced Print & Finishing is both a digital book printer and a full-service commercial printing company. What this means to you is that we can print the covers of your short-run or print-on-demand book on a traditional press. You get the highest quality printing at the same cost and turnaround as digital. As far as we know, we are the only book printer that can offer this advantage at no additional cost. </p>
